Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.22,0:00:21.00,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}挚友啊 挚友啊 在你身上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.00,0:00:23.69,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我看到了令人忧伤的纯粹简单
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.19,0:00:26.90,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}在夕阳西下时的道场一角
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.22,0:00:29.67,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}挥洒着汗水练习刀法
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.20,0:00:33.20,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}挚友啊 挚友啊 在你身上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.20,0:00:35.62,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我看到了引人发笑的满腔热情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.25,0:00:38.95,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}「我也是有梦想的啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.28,0:00:41.80,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}像傻瓜般这样大声叫喊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.72,0:00:46.09,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}若是你所在的街道上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.58,0:00:49.18,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}朝阳东升的话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.80,0:00:52.19,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}想必你会在喧闹的街上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.66,0:00:55.05,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}拼命奔跑着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.77,0:00:58.09,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}若是你所在的街道上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.53,0:01:01.01,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}深夜降临的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.74,0:01:04.11,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}你会穿过宽阔的大道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.56,0:01:06.14,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}在河滩边诉说
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.30,0:01:08.95,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}是这样吧 我的挚友
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.70,0:01:16.58,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}挚友啊 挚友啊 在你身上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.58,0:01:19.22,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我看到了一颗赤子之心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.68,0:01:22.33,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}想必你正守护着重要的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.66,0:01:25.39,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}脸上透露着决心吧
